io.spine.server.storage

Class RecordReadRequest<I>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.storage.RecordReadRequest<I>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the target ID
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadRequest<I>

    @Internal
public final class RecordReadRequest<I>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReadRequest<I>
    A request to read a particular record from RecordStorage.

    A result of this request is a record with the specified ID.

    Two requests are considered equal if they have the same record ID.
